data.description: Lots of updates in this nice home including a newer kitchen with SS appliances, granite counters, pretty cabinets and an updated hall bathroom featuring a soaker tub and separate shower. Large open living/dining area has a fireplace with gas logs and beautiful stamped concrete flooring.  Master ensuite includes a shower and some updates plus new paint. Large laundry room. Enclosed patio with lots of windows plus the backyard features a fire pit and privacy fence. Double car garage. New roof, gutters and exterior paint.  Don't miss out on this well maintained home priced to sell.  Call today for an appointment.
